Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在回想起來，從那天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來過這裏多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，這個星球\N我思念的只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那小小的女朋友，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是我和千瀨的約定之處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在那一天\N從這個地方開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個鄉下地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有什麼樂趣可言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然對未來也是茫茫然的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但唯有一件事\N是我們兩人自己決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個喜歡的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應她，要去她那裏找她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點去吧，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽有我陪著她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心修次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都已經這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的朋友都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易誕生到這世上來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些孩子全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時代一定會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能一直持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次他們現在才要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始他們的時代、世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次那孩子的表情\N越來越堅強了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣\N這一天我們不斷地慰藉彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在疲倦之後\N宛如融合成一個身體似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不分開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偎在一起睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是戀愛的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（第一次紀念修次千瀨）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BC202年 薩瑪之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BC73年 斯巴達克之亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BC66年…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前，不是有人預言\N地球什麼時候會滅亡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候真的相信這種預言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還覺得\N我可能十幾歲就會死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人哭了好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想對那時候的我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟她說「地球不會有事的」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說這種謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我就不用哭得那麼傷心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不用害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9年 托伊頭布加森林之戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:05:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨繼續緩緩的背誦著\N這個星球一個個的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如在悼念死者，為他們送終
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷史教科書的年表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是千瀨唯一拿手的科目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我只是不想想起你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我只是個武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不需要恢復成人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會這麼痛苦，這麼悲傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算變成孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會覺得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候\N我真的希望在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！一定有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣！太可惡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我期待著\N或許愛情可以救得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，現實並沒有讓我獲得解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨還活著，她還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著奮戰到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給了我性愛的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我到最後一刻都要談戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你叫我活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，陪我到這個星球\N滅亡的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易見面了\N可是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，對不起，已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然跟你說這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許你會很震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:08:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在這個城市\N或許感覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是地球的另一端\N真的已經慘不忍賭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類和地球都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城市也快變成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想活下去的國家或是人們\N都到這裏來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個城市有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好傻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我再怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個星球已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好傻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類掙扎到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要這麼做才會甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上會有個超大地震\N一口氣襲擊整個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論再怎麼努力，這個星球\N再過不久就會毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是人類、大家選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我和這個國家的大人物\N很久以前就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以，我真的很想\N把你還有這個城市的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這些我最愛的人\N全部殺光光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球毀滅之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以不會感到疼痛的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以最不痛苦的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為現在的我辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，你卻讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，我會一直看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會離開的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要說什麼要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼要結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要努力到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我會守護這個城鎮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有一點點\N我也會讓他們活到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，因為我是個武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我只會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會連你都殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸，媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸，媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，大家對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海嘯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經守護不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好難過喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想讓他們這麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓他們早點解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們．
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是人，誰都不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸！媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是為了活下去而出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是夢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂，為什麼只有我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它人都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒留下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們留下的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的確曾經存在於這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們小小的\N滑稽又可愛的印證
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，千瀨，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難過吧？很痛苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很寂寞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遵守約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於履行了我跟你的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到了最後\N還是一對戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為變成這樣我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:17:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很…你聽，我真的很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽我說啊，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在呼喚我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在呼喚我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是千瀨要我\N留在這裏的意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只有我一個人得救有什麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我在沒有人的世界\N一個人活下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是啊，千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我說我要陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我叫你活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見你的心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗通噗通的跳著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能存在你的身體裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我全部的能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明保護了你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，不能接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能撫模，也不能做愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後我們可以永遠在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興能夠遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠這樣一直跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜，不要道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，是千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你體內的我怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我在你的心中\N這麼有份量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得見我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修\N千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，聽得見\N我感覺得到你的心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你的心中這麼有份量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們記住所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背負全部的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贖罪到死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是男朋友，她是女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有曇花一現的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都要互相依靠\N一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,個子很小，膽子也很小
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成績也只有中下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有世界史比較強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口頭禪是「對不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座右銘是「我想變得更堅強」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球真的已經毀滅了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯，已經毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球因為懼怕毀滅而發出的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來彷彿像是千瀨的心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是這個星球與我們\N用盡最後力氣所唱出的歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LOVE SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將繼續相戀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,3000)}最終話\N「然後，我們將繼續相戀」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:34.24,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了我心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:40.41,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不想讓這段戀情結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:45.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再見這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:50.95,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,能從這個世上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:55.30,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:19.12,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了我心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:25.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍無法忘懷你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:30.23,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:35.80,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,就要結束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:43.75,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀

